videos.description: With no receiver open, Greg Ward Jr. takes off and lets his speed do the talking getting around the UConn defense to find the end zone and give Houston a 7-0 lead.
videos.headline: Ward shows off the speed for 30-yard TD run

videos.description: Houston looks for the big play running a flea-flicker but it ends with Greg Ward Jr. getting flattened on the play by UConn's Junior Joseph. Ward would return after missing one play.
videos.headline: Ward gets crushed on incomplete flea-flicker

videos.description: Dillon Birden run for 1 yd for a TD
videos.headline: D. Birden run for 1 yd for a TD

videos.description: For the second time in the game, Junior Joseph lays out Greg Ward Jr. but this time the Houston QB finds an open receiver for the touchdown to put the Cougars up 21-0.
videos.headline: Ward gets crushed again, but this time throws TD pass

videos.description: Greg Ward Jr. pass complete to Steven Dunbar for 15 yds for a TD
videos.headline: G. Ward Jr. pass to S. Dunbar for 15 yds for a TD

videos.description: Noel Thomas shows his speed making the catch over the middle and then turning on the jets to outrace the Houston defense for a 62-yard touchdown putting UConn on the board.
videos.headline: UConn strikes back with 62-yard TD to Thomas

videos.description: Greg Ward Jr. run for 10 yds for a TD
videos.headline: Ward runs in for fourth TD of the game

videos.description: Greg Ward Jr. connects with Linell Bonner for the lefty one-handed touchdown catch to put the Cougars up 42-7.
videos.headline: Ward finds Bonner for lefty one-handed TD

videos.description: Houston's Greg Ward Jr. throws a career-high 389 yards and five touchdowns to lead the Cougars past UConn 42-14 on Thursday.
videos.headline: Ward's big performance leads Houston over UConn
